2:T45d,Integrating ISO 9001 QMS standards into your organization's TQM business management system should be comparatively seamless. Therefore, if you currently comply with the ISO 9001 QMS standard, then your organization's process pertaining to Quality Management System or other activities should be very smooth and more economical. Because these processes are already in line with the ISO QMS standards. As such, almost every other functions in the ISO 9001 QMS standard, corresponding to management review, internal audit, and periodic & corrective actions, are shared by ISO 9001 QMS certification standards as well. With seamless and ceaseless improvement and client satisfaction being the centrepiece of both standards (particularly ISO 9001 standard), the “Plan, Do, Check & Act” cycle will the typical theme for any organization. Now, it becomes very much clear that these two ISO standards are closely connected. Given TQM’s basis of integration of systems ultimately resulting in client satisfaction which makes it evident that ISO 9001 certification or implementation has a role to play within this system.0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How can ISO 14001 help to enhance your organization's TQM"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:31+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"How can ISO 14001 help to enhance your organization's TQM\n\n      Title\n\nEnhancing Total Quality Management with ISO 9001 | Relation between ISO QMS and"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How can ISO 14001 help to enhance your organization's TQM"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Title"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Enhancing Total Quality Management with ISO 9001 | Relation between ISO QMS and TQM | Wizms"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Meta Description"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In this blog, we will discuss How can ISO 9001 Quality Management System (QMS) enhance an organization's Total Quality Management. In real time, it will be clear that there are several activities followed as a result of implementing ISO 9001 which are capable of improving “total quality management” (TQM) of an organization."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"While ISO 9001 certification and standard is well known because almost every business sector’s foremost standard to enable an organization to manage quality performance and process, there are also other added benefits that organizations might accrue from implementing ISO 9001 QMS standard and its practices. In this blog, we will discuss How can ISO 9001 Quality Management System (QMS) enhance an organization's Total Quality Management. In real time, it will be clear that there are several activities and practices followed as a result of implementing ISO 9001 standards which are capable of improving “total quality management” (TQM) of an organization. Therefore, it would appear rational to assume that the implementation of ISO 9001 certification could result in enhancements in overall quality management and performance. Let us delve into how can ISO 9001 certification for an organization improve total quality management."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Relation between ISO 9001 and Total Quality Management"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"$2"}],"$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9"]}],"$La"]}]}],["$Lb"],"$Lc"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
3:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How can ISO 9001 QMS standard assist to improve your organization's TQM and performance?"}]
4:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"If your organization abide by ISO 9001 certification and if it incorporates a functioning QMS (Quality Management System), then this without a doubt will absolutely influence your organization's overall quality performance. Let’s take a look how:"}]
5:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Your organization will be familiar with the ISO 9001 QMS standard's objectives and key performance indicators (KPIs) as well. As much as fact-based decision making is significant to Total Quality Management (TQM), using a similar basic and fundamental methodologies to determine the quality KPIs and working towards quality targets can be vital in understanding your performance, and ultimately enhancing it."}]
6:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Measuring training efficiency and the importance of training and implementing ISO 9001 QMS standard in your organization can be equally vital to your QMS (Quality Management System), an integrated TQM system. With the combined aspects of quality performance, product knowledge and shared TQM's or QMS's objectives into your training program, you'll be able to increase awareness and assist to improve product knowledge and QMS performance very efficiently. Effective ISO 9001 QMS training will facilitate this."}]
7:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Leverage the authorities and leaders to enhance quality. It is regarded as the best way to demonstrate leadership in line with the ISO 9001 QMS standard. Because of the positive impact that noteworthy leadership skills can bring. As it will improve your organization's overall performance, and this is also the case with ISO 9001 QMS standard. Most leaders will always look at the chances of enhancing quality performance with comparatively very minimal expenditure. Thus, implementing quality-related activities into your existing ISO 9001 QMS functions will provide immediate advantages to the quality performance of your business. It is best advised to draft an idea or plan how these activities can be replicated or just extended to improve your organization’s quality management performance."}]
8:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Since we have established excellent leadership skills and configured KPIs, it is recommended by top ISO certification consultants to embody basic quality management responsibilities to an individual's job descriptions. As this will present your organization with a crystal clear opportunity to integrate activities, programs, and associated responsibilities into the roles and responsibilities of designated people, who will then be trained and mentored to properly perform activities that may improve your product quality internally, and deliver impeccable TQM results."}]
9:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Work to alter the organization's working culture. A culture of positive behaviour which can improve your organization's total quality management performance can also be established simultaneously. Reinforcing that sensible quality management, product performance, and client satisfaction all result in augmented success for the organization and increased job security for workers will be the inspiration for culture reinforcement. This could typically result in enhanced worker activity in terms of employee interest in quality management, and inclination to interact in improvement meetings and forums. Therefore, if you have established and improved this culture using the recommendation given during ISO 9001 QMS implementation, your organization should have a sound basis to use this component to boost all-round quality management performance."}]
